creator: Lawtech365
descriptionHtml:
"Lawyer 365 gives you access to free legal information services, legal template documents and free appointments with qualified lawyers, straight from your phone.

Lawyer 365 lets you see a lawyer by video from home, work or on-the-go, 7 days a week, 365 days a year. You can get a free appointment within minutes or book up to a week ahead, all from the comfort of your home.

Legal document templates include hundreds of editable agreements and contracts to enable you to protect your business and keep up with your legal and compliance requirements.

BOOK A FREE LEGAL CONSULTATION

Simply download the app, enter your details, select a lawyer and get free initial legal advice by video, phone or chat, all through the Lawyer 365 app.

You can consult with hundreds of lawyers, free of charge, at a time that suits you. The lawyer will call you within the app to start your free legal consultation.

OUR LAWYERS ARE HERE FOR YOU

High quality initial legal advice is available to anyone, wherever you live. Just register in minutes and see how it can work for you:

-  See a lawyer the same day, even outside of practice opening hours

-  Have your appointment anywhere in the world

-  Get initial expert legal advice free of charge

-  Download editable legal templates, agreements and contracts

LEGAL HELP CHAT

Our Artificial Intelligence Legal Assistant (AILA) has the ability to recognise most of the standard legal questions and suggest possible next steps.

Alternatively, use the Live Chat feature to ask legal questions and get answers from a member of our team, straight from your phone.

YOU’RE IN SAFE HANDS

Lawyers listed on the Lawyer 365 platform are all experienced, qualified and registered lawyers in their relevant jurisdictions who have undergone training in the latest video consultation techniques.

So, what are you waiting for – talk to a lawyer within minutes, 24/7. It’s free."
